casebody.data:
No. 276,

Misc.

Rexford v. Florida. Petitioner pro se. James W. Kynes, Attorney General of Florida, and George R. Georgieff, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Motion for leave, to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
